info.description:
This plugin is used to set the meta tags in templates. Possible values are:
{{Meta|Title}}
{{Meta|Description}}
{{Meta|Keywords}}
{{Meta|Robots}}
{{Meta|Properties}} – e.g. Open Graph Tags
{{Meta|CanonicalURL}}
{{Meta|ThemeURL}} – route to the currently used theme
{{Meta|RootURL}} – route to the home page
